  "instructions": [
    "1. In a large bowl, mix together mashed avocado, flour, crunchy festive nuts, egg, salt, and pepper until a thick batter forms.",
    "2. Heat a non-stick frying pan with stir-fry vegetable oil over medium heat.",
    "3. Using a spoon, drop small amounts of the avocado mixture into the pan, flattening slightly into patties.",
    "4. Cook for 2-3 minutes on each side, or until golden brown and crispy.",
    "5. Remove from heat and drain on paper towels.",
    "6. Serve warm and enjoy!"
